/>\n而家Roy Moore在鐵票倉敗北, Trump跟此次失敗脫不了關係</blockquote>"},{"pid":"73c380454c823a2a029a59d7e03d8e8f55581a4d","tid":497924,"uid":123264,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T10:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以後既選舉方程式:<br />\n囉二百萬出黎,搵十個同參選者有接觸既白左神經女人,一人比二十萬,買通媒體開記者會<br />\n對面係甘迺迪都輸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTrump上次面對類似指控都贏<br />\n<br />\n只係Trump以為佢上次無事, Roy Moore都會無事... Trump又真係走去訓身撐Roy Moore, 點知....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔訓身撐坐係度等死咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有Trump馬仔曾提議佢唔會出聲, 但Trump堅持親自支持Roy Moore.... <br />\n<br />\n而家Roy Moore在鐵票倉敗北, Trump跟此次失敗脫不了關係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地一有事就同佢割席<br />\n無恥政客咪呢d囉<br />\n可惜弱智仔中意無恥既人"},{"pid":"eacae060bb968301fa9711b653b547c1495cd4cd","tid":497924,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.thenewslens.com/article/85380\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F85380&d=lSY63ykJtQQRdnDxcTQr6JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=0f678796\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.thenewslens.com/article/85380</a><br />\n<br />\n阿拉巴馬州被視為「深紅」州份，共和黨支持者眾。2016年美國總統大選中，共和黨的特朗普在阿拉巴馬州獲得62%選票，民主黨的希拉莉則只獲得34%選票。塞申斯自1996年起連續4次當選該州聯邦參議員，同屬共和黨的謝爾比（Richard Shelby）更於1992年起連續5次當選。"},{"pid":"cf4d68851a9e1be1bf100aac562d50b31df5911b","tid":497924,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:27:48.000Z","msg":"逼害Trump Trump 啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：撐Hillary"},{"pid":"2f4e6aafb3ae7d0dd9ffe224ebcb4b72c2daf842","tid":497924,"uid":78662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以後既選舉方程式:<br />\n囉二百萬出黎,搵十個同參選者有接觸既白左神經女人,一人比二十萬,買通媒體開記者會<br />\n對面係甘迺迪都輸</blockquote><br />\n無記左甘乃迪係輸總vote 數，贏選舉人票既<img src=\"/assets